Once upon a time, Red Demon and Blue Demon lived in the mountains of Japan.
Red Demon wanted to be friends with children.
So he put a board in front of his house.
He wrote these words on the board: "Open house. Please come in."
But everyone was afraid of him, so no one came in.
He felt sad and finally took the board away.
Red Demon and Blue Demon lived in a city in Japan.
Red Demon wanted to be friends with children.
Blue Demon put a board in front of Red Demon's house.
No one came to Red Demon's house.
Red Demon took the board away.
